title: american horror story coven - Marie laveau tells the truth about hank
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: The best things in this scene is when Fiona flips her hair before she slaps Cordelia, and how Marie sees her coming and is just like, yeet!
at least Marie helped Cordelia get up.
I love how she really sets Marie Laveau straight. She says it point blank: Witch hunters kill witches... you are, in fact, a witch.
Cordelia had that coming. When the Supreme tells you to not trust someone because she can sense dishonesty, you listen.
description:
american horror story coven -  Marie laveau tells the truth about hank/ Fiona lashes out at Cordelia 
3x10 the magical delights of Stevie nicks
